    "content": "<p>For the square steel beam cross-section shown in the figure, the shape factor about Z - Z axis is S and the plastic moment capacity is M<sub>p</sub>. Consider yield stress f<sub>y</sub> = 250 MPa and a = 100 mm.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m0t284wd/fd780280-002b-417d-acd3-b26afa6ed643/d6f287d0-6d98-11ef-917d-3fcf65870137/file-jaoe38c1m0t284we.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m0t284wd/fd780280-002b-417d-acd3-b26afa6ed643/d6f287d0-6d98-11ef-917d-3fcf65870137/file-jaoe38c1m0t284we.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2022 Set 2 Structural Analysis - Plastic Analysis Question 2 English\"></p>\n<p>The values of S and M<sub>p</sub> (rounded off to one decimal place) are</p>",
    "options": [
      {
        "identifier": "A",
        "content": "S = 2.0, M<sub>p</sub> = 100.2 kN-m"
